# ============================================
# Environment Variables (SECURITY - Never commit actual secrets)
# ============================================
# Block all .env files across the repository (recursive)
# Glob pattern **/ matches all subdirectories at any depth
# Examples covered:
#   - .env, backend/.env, frontend/.env
#   - backend/config/.env, backend/services/auth/.env
