# ============================================
# Pattern Testing Examples
# ============================================
# To test if a file would be ignored, use:
#   git check-ignore -v <filepath>
# Examples:
#   git check-ignore -v backend/.env
#   git check-ignore -v backend/.env.example
#   git check-ignore -v mongodb-win32-x86_64-windows-9.0.0/

# ============================================
# DO NOT IGNORE - Explicit Exceptions
# ============================================
# These patterns override earlier ignore rules
!.gitignore
!README.md
!**/.env.example
!**/.env.*.example
